{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We're going for several days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'm not sure of the date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We arrive in a place we never heard of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The place is called Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We get off the train in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We're lined up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We're-- they always marched us like soldiers would march.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they would always say, left, right, left, 1, 2, 3.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we would have to walk that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They walked-- they walked us into the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we're assigned to-- to barracks again, what they call blocks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And each block had what they called the [NON-ENGLISH], which was the guy who was in charge of that particular barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And from there on, from there on on, nobody is-- nobody is called by name anymore at this point.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Everybody is called by their number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They called us [NON-ENGLISH], which means prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And if they called somebody, they would say, [NON-ENGLISH] number so and so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And if you were that number, you knew they were calling you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, we're in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Same things with the [NON-ENGLISH] every morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We're standing there, whether you're sick, whether you drop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "You have to stand on that [NON-ENGLISH] in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Same kind of food, they give us a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "The end of the day, you get a watered-down type of soup called kohlrabi soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We're not working at this point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They took us all in-- they took pictures of each one of us from the chest up, like a prisoner would have, like you see here in-- like you see here in the post office, for example.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Why, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "We never saw those pictures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "But they took pictures of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
